# ============================================================================
# NOTES FOR CONTRIBUTORS
# ============================================================================
#
# Before committing:
# 1. Check .env files are ignored: git status should NOT show .env.prod
# 2. Verify no logs are staged: git status should NOT show .log files
# 3. Confirm no personal data: Review files before git add
# 4. Use git check-ignore to test patterns: git check-ignore -v filename
#
# To see what's ignored:
#   git status --ignored
#
# To test if a file would be ignored:
#   git check-ignore -v path/to/file
#
# To override .gitignore (NOT recommended for sensitive files):
#   git add -f path/to/file
#
# ============================================================================
